      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive rod bearing service and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Double VANOS system is fully operational, providing optimal cam phasing across the entire rev range. While the aesthetic condition is consistent with regular use, the mechanical synchronization and suspension kinematics remain tight, offering the precise, analog feedback enthusiasts demand.",
